{"pid":"bacf8818a56398bec3fa1a3a20a4835ce686c68c","tid":2022863,"uid":173179,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:39:11.000Z","msg":"中國牛肉有毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想反抗既話要唱好唱埋"},{"pid":"c9a4964539c06686fc07071f9d1fca0be4f1976b","tid":2022863,"uid":81756,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:43:44.000Z","msg":"然後其他國家入澳洲大麥再賣俾中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fce5327e37558669d8eb9a03903d285f6c8877e","tid":2022863,"uid":67468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9a4964539c06686fc07071f9d1fca0be4f1976b","tid":2022863,"uid":81756,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:43:44.000Z","msg":"然後其他國家入澳洲大麥再賣俾中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:44:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd627740568eaf3253f7011d56370b5ed32555e2","tid":2022863,"uid":321374,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:47:38.000Z","msg":"點解唔cut埋奧洲進口既鐵礦?"},{"pid":"e105f255131a37e158674d6e76595d503437b5e8","tid":2022863,"uid":276723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:48:16.000Z","msg":"轉口香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0794b12338eb2c6ead4e2ab543d8f1cfeb2e7c5b","tid":2022863,"uid":163841,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:49:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.toutiao.com/a1666984003175436/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.toutiao.com%2Fa1666984003175436%2F&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCpriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=3d695287\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.toutiao.com/a1666984003175436/</a><br />\n<br />\n家裡小麥全完了，今年沒有麥子吃了。我給老媽說，沒事，我們抗的過去。<br />\n<br />\n昨天晚上山東部分地區突發大冰雹，我的老家山東青島萊西就是比較嚴重的地方，當時電閃雷鳴，伴有十級大風，大小如鴿子蛋的冰雹下了足足十分鐘，就是這十分鐘讓我們村損失慘重。<br />\n<br />\n還有一個月就到小麥的收割季節了，今天早上我媽去麥田看了一下，全部倒下了，今年不用收麥子了，一顆不剩，村裡情況都差不多，有極個別的位置好一些，還能剩下一點麥子。還好我們家有餘量，明年的麥子也夠吃了。<br />\n<br />\n村裡種桃樹的叔叔，家裡5畝桃子，落滿了一地，損失5萬多。還有我們村很多種甜瓜的，正是大量上市的季節，大部分被打碎了，今年真的太難了，本以為在農村好過一些，這一場冰雹，讓大家剛看到的希望又被澆滅了。<br />\n<br />\n還好我們那邊政府都給農民的小麥買了保險，不知道一畝小麥保險公司給賠多少錢。<br />\n<br />\n祈禱我們都能挺過去，一切會好起來的！"},{"pid":"7f8530edfe0132b653ac051d64db376ab9abff5a","tid":2022863,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b33c0431b1ef36cece0a099b55ac5d42ae0281dc","tid":2022863,"uid":302,"like":96,"dislike":1,"score":95,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T14:54:54.000Z","msg":"繼續去做 放膽去做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:51:47.000Z","msg":"下個到美帝<br />\n打擊蘋果 高通"},{"pid":"13e3a8e70508bca96c0311fa4a0eba2f24d5feb9","tid":2022863,"uid":261913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:53:09.000Z","msg":"今次真係隊足一年草<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3baac30beebff88903b588d01821fe268ce0de5c","tid":2022863,"uid":143747,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:54:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3hLNd1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3hLNd1f.jpg&h=906ccdbb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bda1ea7c1b361414d75b5e58da21f13a08745f65","tid":2022863,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:55:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支持中國"},{"pid":"338aeac20a91a76cef8ce5cffc7287a730f3db97","tid":2022863,"uid":37912,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T06:04:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"797dda9ea5e221156be67f45acb20a3371816249","tid":2022863,"uid":68463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20